{"tid":220766,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"一次過得罪兩大宗教！《街霸 5》被發現佛廟場景誤用伊斯蘭教聲效","createTime":"2017-04-28T08:02:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-29T12:32:10.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1a057b1bf5b020f900a129ed4123d3eceabc669b","tid":220766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T08:02:30.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>一次過得罪兩大宗教！《街霸 5》被發現佛廟場景誤用伊斯蘭教聲效<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/04/28/street-fighter-5-temple-hideout-wrong-bg/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F04%2F28%2Fstreet-fighter-5-temple-hideout-wrong-bg%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=6c9c308c\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/04/28/street-fighter-5-temple-hideout-wrong-bg/game-channel/</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n格鬥遊戲《Street Fighter》的開發商 Capcom，將經典《街霸 2》的泰國舞台重新製作，並且以「Temple Hideout」名義在最新的《Street Fighter 5》上推出。這個舞台版面原本以 in-store 購買的方式於 PS4 和 PC 版推出，不過上架僅一天就被 Capcom 緊急拿下。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4qZJtHj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4qZJtHj.jpg&h=b9ce11fe&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n正當不少人對此覺得奇怪的時候，有玩家發現 Capcom 或者犯下了一個頗嚴重的錯誤，導致 Temple Hideout 雖然下架。有玩家發現 Capcom 在泰國的佛教寺廟中，錯誤地使用了伊斯蘭教的禱告聲效作為背景音樂，明顯地聽到格格不入的阿拉伯語，這樣對兩個宗教都有不敬之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://youtu.be/D_AEkLRBBGU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FD_AEkLRBBGU&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdYM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=ebce111e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/D_AEkLRBBGU</a></div><br />\n<br />\nCapcom 及後發表聲明承認 Temple Hideout 使用了錯誤的背景音樂，無意地產生了宗教上的誤會。Capcom 表示當發現問題後，馬上終止該 DLC 的分發，並且決定在短期內進行緊急的伺服器維修更新，以修正背景音效的錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n來源：polygon"},{"pid":"f7e959c675e5fa569ee9ab2adc66a5ebda5c92f4","tid":220766,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6b652b5165659487060c9fbf5ff6a2c452ecd6","tid":220766,"uid":36035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T12:32:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}